com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os.validation
Interface AIXLocalUserValidator

public interface AIXLocalUserValidator

A sample validator interface for AIXLocalUser. This doesn't really do anything, and it's not a real EMF artifact. It was generated by the org.eclipse.emf.examples.generator.validator plug-in to illustrate how EMF's code generator can be extended. This can be disabled with -vmargs -Dorg.eclipse.emf.examples.generator.validator=false.
